The crucial book on Iraq for antiwar activists is <i><a href="http://www.amazon.com/gp/redirect.html?ie=UTF8&amp;location=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.com%2FIraq-Withdrawal-American-Empire-Project%2Fdp%2F0805082727%2Fsr%3D8-2%2Fqid%3D1169001703%3Fie%3DUTF8%26amp%3Bs%3Dbooks&amp;tag=socialistwork-20&amp;linkCode=ur2&amp;c" target="_blank">Iraq: The Logic of Withdrawal</a>,</i> recently republished in an updated paperback edition from the American Empire Project with a foreword by Howard Zinn.<p>
